        "richtext_Gbedat": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For residents of {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }} seeking something truly unique, Griffin & Co offers a bespoke design experience that transforms your ideas into tangible heirlooms. </p><p>We believe there is nothing quite like having a piece of jewellery designed exclusively for you.</p>",
