        "text": "<p>While our Chichester showroom is the heart of our design process, we understand that some clients prefer the security and comfort of their own environment.</p><p>For custom jewellery commissions, we offer a <strong>Private Home Visit</strong> service throughout {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. Our lead designer will visit you to discuss your ideas and take precise measurements.</p>",
